Package com.github.wuic.resource.impl

This package defines different implements of a WuicResource.

          Description

Class Summary
AbstractWuicResource Base implementation of the WuicResource interface.
AbstractWuicResourceFactory Abstract implementation of what is a AbstractWuicResourceFactory.DefaultWuicResourceFactory.
AbstractWuicResourceFactory.DefaultWuicResourceFactory Factory that produces resource with a path which matches or contains one occurrence of the given path.
AbstractWuicResourceFactory.RegexWuicResourceFactory Factory that produces resource with a path considered as a regular expression.
AbstractWuicResourceFactoryBuilder Abstract implementation of what is a WuicResourceFactoryBuilder.
ByteArrayWuicResource Represents an in-memory resource.
HttpWuicResource A WuicResource implementation for HTTP accesses.
